20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62e96c2a57dd3c0018dc1392%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELauren%20Dana%2FInsider%3B%20Physicians%20Formula%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20I%20noticed%20about%20this%20lip%20plumper%20was%20how%20sweet%20it%20smelled%20(literally%20like%20a%20marshmallow).%20About%20three%20minutes%20after%20I%20swiped%20on%20the%20product%2C%20I%20noticed%20a%20cooling%20sensation.%20About%20a%20minute%20later%2C%20I%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20by%20the%20size%20of%20my%20now-juicy%20lips%20in%20my%20iPhone%20camera.%20However%2C%20the%20swelling%20went%20down%20about%2010%20to%2015%20minutes%20later%2C%20although%20the%20glossy%20sheen%20remained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrande%20Cosmetics%20GrandeLIPS%20Hydrating%20Lip%20Plumper%20Gloss%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20collage.%20Left%20side%20depicts%20a%20close%20up%20selfie%20of%20a%20person%20staring%20at%20the%20camera%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20display%20their%20use%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CGrande%20Cosmetics%20GrandeLIPS%20Hydrating%20Lip%20Plumper%20Gloss%E2%80%9D%20Right%20slide%20illustrates%20a%20gold%20container%20of%20the%20product%20%E2%80%9CGrande%20Cosmetics%20GrandeLIPS%20Hydrating%20Lip%20Plumper%20Gloss.%E2%80%9D%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62e96fb360b2000018720031%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELauren%20Dana%2FInsider%3B%20Grande%20Cosmetics%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20GrandeLIPS%20Hydrating%20Lip%20Plumper%20Gloss%20is%20among%20Grande%20Cosmetics'%20most%20popular%20products%20%E2%80%94%20and%20for%20good%20reason.%20Although%20the%20swelling%20started%20almost%20immediately%2C%20the%20pr