eing%20a%20spectator%20all%20the%20more%20uncomfortable%20and%20compelling.%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EPH%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%26quot%3BSilo%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221331%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Common%20in%20%26quot%3BSilo%2C%26quot%3B%20now%20streaming%20on%20Apple%20TV%2B.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dbda7d4ef9f30019f78e59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22999%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECommon%20in%20%26quot%3BSilo%2C%26quot%3B%20now%20streaming%20on%20Apple%20TV%2B.%3Cp%3EApple%20TV%2B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20TV%2B%20has%20quietly%20been%20making%20some%20of%20the%20most%20brilliant%20shows%20of%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20including%20%26quot%3BFor%20All%20Mankind%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BTed%20Lasso%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Morning%20Show.%26quot%3B%20The%20streamer%20has%20served%20up%20another%20new%20captivating%20story%20with%20%26quot%3BSilo.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20Hugh%20Howey's%20%26quot%3BWool%26quot%3B%20novels%2C%20the%20show%20revolves%20around%20an%20underground%20bunker%20that%20houses%20thousands%20of%20survivors%2C%20while%20the%20outside%20world%20has%20been%20ravaged%20by%20nuclear%20war.%20After%20a%20brief%20introduction%20to%20the%20Silo%20and%20the%20struggles%20of%20bunker%20life%2C%20it%20quickly%20segues%20into%20a%20murder-mystery%20%E2%80%94%20which%20feels%20unique%20in%20the%20post-apocalyptic%20setting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEngineer%20Juliette%20Nichols%20(Rebecca%20Ferguson)%20is%20the%20one%20in%20charge%20of%20figuring%20out%20the%20motive%20behind%20the%20murder%20and%20how%20it%20connects%20to%20the%20secrecy%20surrounding%20the%20outside%20world.%20Ferguson%20carries%20the%20show%20on%20her%20shoulders%20with%20ease%2C%20nailing%20Nichols'%20dedicated%20sense%20of%20duty%20to%20her%20jobs%20in%20the%20Silo%20and%20to%20the%20people%20she%20loves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20bunker%20is%20huge%20(and%20the%20sets%20are%20equally%20impressive)%20the%20cinematography%20ensures%20that%20it%20always%20feels%20claustrophobic%20and%20grimy.%20If%20that%20wasn't%20enough%2C%20this%20post-apocalyptic%20procedural%20even%20has%20plenty%20of%20subtext%20and%20commentary%20lurking%20below%20the%20surface%20about%20authority%2C%20fascism%2C%20and%20socialism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStellar%20performances%2C%20great%20writing%2C%20and%20fascinating%20world-building%20make%20%26quot%3BSilo%26quot%3B%20a%20very%20rewarding%20watch.%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EEJ%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%26quot%3BStar%20Wars%3A%20Visions%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221688%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22star%20wars%20visions%20season%202%20key%20art%20showing%20characters%20from%20the%20show's%20second%20season%20imposed%20within%20a%20brushstroke%20number%202%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dbd8b65e5d5a00195eb0fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221267%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BStar%20Wars%3A%20Visions%26quot%3B%20season%20two%20brought%20new%20animation%20studios%20into%20the%20Star%20Wars%20universe.%3Cp%3EDisney%2B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20settings%20far%20away%20from%20the%20main%20film%20franchise%2C%20%26quot%3BStar%20Wars%3A%20Visions%26quot%3B%20moves%20away%20from%20aimless%20space%20battles%20and%20reasserts%20the%20core%20tenets%20of%20the%20franchise%20with%20beautiful%20tales%20about%20hope%20(%26quot%3BIn%20The%20Stars%26quot%3B)%2C%20unity%20against%20injustice%20(%26quot%3BThe%20Pit%26quot%3B)%2C%20the%20eternal%20balance%20between%20good%20and%20evil%20(%26quot%3BJourney%20to%20the%20Dark%20Head%26quot%3B)%2C%20and%20so%20much%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20tale%20in%20the%20animated%20anthology%20series%2C%20created%20by%20studios%20around%20the%20world%2C%20is%20elevated%20by%20its%20distinct%20animation%20style%2C%20ranging