0have%20been%20made%2C%20which%20do%20not%20reflect%20the%20factual%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20points%20that%20the%20finance%20ministry%20has%20raised%20is%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20India's%20general%20government%20debt%2C%20which%20includes%20those%20of%20the%20Centre%20and%20states%2C%20is%20in%20rupees%2C%20and%20external%20borrowings%20make%20up%20only%20a%20small%20portion.%20It%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20rollover%20risk%20is%20low%20for%20domestic%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20Article%20IV%20consultations%20with%20India%2C%20the%20IMF%20had%20said%20that%2C%20under%20adverse%20shocks%2C%20the%20country's%20general%20government%20debt%20could%20be%20100%25%20of%20debt%20to%20GDP%20ratio%20by%20FY%202028.%20The%20ministry%20has%20clarified%20that%20this%20was%20mentioned%20as%20an%20extreme%20possibility%20like%20%26quot%3Bonce-in-a-century%20Covid-19%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20among%20various%20favourable%20and%20unfavourable%20scenarios%20that%20were%20listed.%20The%20ministry%20has%20emphasised%20that%20in%20that%20instance%2C%20the%20IMF%20was%20talking%20only%20of%20a%20worst-case%20scenario%20and%20this%20is%20not%20a%20%26quot%3Bfait%20accompli%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20finance%20ministry%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20IMF%20reports%20for%20other%20countries%20showed%20a%20much%20higher%20extreme%20scenario%20for%20them%2C%20with%20the%20figures%20being%20160%25%20for%20the%20US%2C%20140%25%20for%20the%20UK%20and%20200%25%20for%20China.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F1t23cpgo_dept-to-gdp-chart_625x300_22_December_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMF%20report%20for%20India%20also%20indicates%20that%2C%20under%20favourable%20circumstances%2C%20the%20General%20Government%20Debt%20to%2