-create-5-cr-jobs-gadkari-123122200894_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fev-sales-likely-to-reach-1-cr-annually-by-2030-create-5-cr-jobs-gadkari-123122200894_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fev-sales-likely-to-reach-1-cr-annually-by-2030-create-5-cr-jobs-gadkari-123122200894_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Wayfair%20CEO%20Calls%20For%20Longer%20Work%20Hours%3A%20%26quot%3BWinning%20Requires%20Hard%20Work%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENiraj%20Shah%2C%20Indian-American%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20(CEO)%20of%20online%20furniture%20firm%20Wayfair%2C%20curated%20a%20special%20message%20for%20his%20employees%20after%20the%20company%20yielded%20profitable%20results.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3ECNN%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20his%20note%20to%20employees%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20not%20only%20encouraged%20employees%20to%20work%20hard%20and%20be%20ambitious%20but%20also%20asked%20them%20to%20do%20more%20work%20and%20blend%20%26quot%3Bwork%20with%20life%26quot%3B.%20He%20told%20them%20to%20not%20shy%20away%20from%20working%20long%20hours%20and%20added%20that%20there%20was%20no%20historical%20evidence%20which%20showed%20laziness%20led%20to%20success.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWinning%20requires%20hard%20work.%20I%20believe%20that%20most%20of%20us%2C%20being%20ambitious%20individuals%2C%20find%20fulfilment%20in%20the%20joy%20of%20seeing%20our%20efforts%20materialize%20into%20tangible%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20said%20in%20a%20note%20to%20employees%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F12%2F21%2Fbusiness%2Fwayfair-ceo-workers-hours%2Findex.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECNN%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWorking%20long%20hours%2C%20being%20responsive%2C%20blending%20work%20and%20life%2C%20is%20not%20anything%20to%20shy%20away%20from.%20There%20is%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20history%20of%20laziness%20being%20rewarded%20with%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2023%2F12%2F20%2Fwayfair-ceo-niraj-shah-warns-staff-laziness-rewarded-success-profitability%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFortune%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20also%20added%20that%20the%20idea%20staff%20should%20not%20work%20was%20%26quot%3Blaughably%20false%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BHard%20work%20is%20essential%20for%20success%2C%20and%20a%20key%20part%20of%20getting%20things%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20deserves%20to%20have%20a%20great%20personal%20life%20-%20everyone%20manages%20that%20in%20their%20own%20way%20-%20ambitious%20people%20find%20ways%20to%20blend%20and%20balance%20the%20two%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20letter%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20also%20encouraged%20Wayfair%20employees%20to%20think%20of%20the%20company%20money%20they%20spend%20as%20their%20own%20and%20negotiate%20prices.%20%26quot%3BWould%20you%20spend%20money%20on%20that%2C%20would%20you%20spend%20that%20much%20money%20for%20that%20thing%2C%20does%20that%20price%20seem%20reasonable%2C%20and%20lastly%20-%20have%20you%20negotiated%20the%20price%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian-American%20CEO%20told%20employees%20in%20his%20email%20that%20the%20company%20is%20back%20to%20being%20profitable.%20%26quot%3BTogether%20we%20can%20win%20much%20faster%20than%20we%20are%20winning%20now%20if%20we%20all%20row%20in%20this%20direction%20together.%20Let's%20be%20aggressive%2C%20pragmatic%2C%20frugal%2C%20agile%2C%20customer-oriented%2C%20and%20smart%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fex-ceo-of-tech-mahindra-shares-valuable-insights-as-he-announces-retirement-from-corporate-life-4716806%5C%22%3EEx%20CEO%20Of%20Tech%20Mahindra%20Shares%20Valuable%20Insights%20As%20He%20Announces%20Retirement%20From%20Corporate%20Life%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20users%20called%20Mr%20Shah's%20note%20%26quot%3Btoxic%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20basically%20saying%20if%20you%20don't%20work%20late%20then%20you're%20lazy.%20Long%20hours%20don't%20prove%20anything%20about%20productivity.%20It%20just%20means%20you%20worked%20long%20hours!%26quot%3B%20wrote%20one%20Reddit%20user.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20when%20these%20CEOs%20talk%20about%20'winning'%20as%20if%20the%20employees%20get%20absolutely%20anything%20out%20of%20the%20company's%20profitability%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20actually%20being%20compensated%20for%20your%20time%2C%20sure.%20If%20you're%20making%20an%20average%20salary%20but%20dealing%20with%20corporate%20BS%2C%20move%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20expressed%20a%20third.%20%26quot%3BI'll%20sacrifice%20the%20life%20in%20work-life%20balance%20when%20the%20paycheck%20reflects%20that%20it%20is%20worth%20it.%20I%20doubt%20it%20is%20for%20anyone%20he%20is%20giving%20this%20lecture%20to%20(that%20he%20probably%20thinks%20is%20SO%20inspirational).%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20is%20not%20the%20first%20CEO%20to%20glamourise%20overworking.%20Earlier%2C%20Infosys%20founder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-suggests-70-hour-work-week-to-youngsters-sparks-debate-4516739%5C%22%3ENR%20Narayana%20Murthy%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20India's%20work%20culture%20needs%20to%20change%20and%20youngsters%20should%20be%20prepared%20to%20work%20for%2070%20hours%20a%20week%20if%20the%20country%20has%20to%20compete%20effectively%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%20He%20stated%20that%20India's%20work%20productivity%20is%20one%20of%20the%20lowest%20in%20the%20world%20and%20asked%20the%20youth%20the%20contribute%20