ir%20of%20the%20Governor%2C%20the%20person%20concerned%20should%20consult%20with%20the%20former%20Governor%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Satyapal%20Malik.%20He%20will%20get%20an%20information%20about%20Pulwama%2C%20and%20more%20things%20related%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%26quot%3B%20TMC%20spokesperson%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBengal%20is%20the%20safest%20according%20to%20central%20government%20reports.%20Kolkata%20is%20the%20safest%20city%20and%20Bengal%20is%20the%20safest%20state.%20Unfortunate%20incidents%2C%20planned%20incidents%20are%20happening%20against%20women%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20So%20he%20should%20not%20misuse%20his%20Chair%20like%20a%20BJP%20cadre%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ghosh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20was%20speaking%20at%20an%20event%20organised%20by%20the%20Calcutta%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20-%20a%20special%20session%20on%20the%20scope%20of%20industry%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInviting%20industrialists%20to%20the%20Valley%2C%20Mr%20Sinha%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20perception%20that%20investments%20mostly%20come%20to%20Jammu.%20But%20I%20want%20to%20clarify%20that%20in%20the%20planned%20investment%20of%20Rs%2090%2C000%20crore%20is%20almost%20equal%20in%20both%20places.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20assure%20you%20there%20is%20a%20better%20climate%20(of%20investment)%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20I%20am%20not%20making%20a%20political%20statement.%20But%20if%20you%20come%20there%2C%20you%20will%20experience%20it%20yourself%20and%20say%20it%20louder%20than%20me.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20verdict%20on%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20given%20its%20stamp%20of%20approval%20to%20what%20Parliament%20did%20on%20August%205%2C%202019.%20It%20is%20a%20tradition%