.%20How%20you%20dress%20and%20what%20you%20eat%20is%20your%20choice.%20Why%20should%20I%20obstruct%20you%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20while%20addressing%20a%20gathering%20in%20Mysore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Siddaramaiah%20said%20that%20people%20in%20the%20state%20were%20free%20to%20wear%20and%20eat%20whatever%20they%20choose%20to.%20%26quot%3BWear%20what%20you%20want.%20Eat%20what%20you%20want.%20I%20will%20eat%20what%20I%20want%2C%20you%20eat%20what%20you%20want.%20I%20wear%20dhoti%2C%20you%20wear%20pant%20shirt.%20What's%20wrong%20in%20that%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20under%20Chief%20Minister%20B%20Bommai%20had%20banned%20the%20head%20covering%20in%20educational%20institutes%20of%20the%20state%20leading%20to%20a%20massive%20row.%20After%20several%20students%20moved%20the%20court%20against%20the%20ban%2C%C2%A0the%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20upheld%20the%20state's%20ban%2C%20saying%20that%20wearing%20a%20hijab%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20an%20essential%20religious%20practice%20of%20Islam%26quot%3B%20and%20educational%20institutes%20can%20decide%20the%20dress%20code%20for%20all%20their%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20went%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%C2%A0delivered%20a%20split%20verdict%2C%20with%20one%20judge%20maintaining%20that%20the%20state%20is%20authorised%20to%20enforce%20uniform%20in%20schools%20and%20the%20other%20describing%20hijab%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20after%20the%20Congress%20government%20was%20voted%20to%20power%2C%20Karnataka%20minister%20Priyank%20Kharge%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bany%20law%26quot%3B%20brought%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%26quot%3B%20which%20was%20deemed%20%26quot%3Bregressive%26quot%3B%20would%20be%20repealed%20by%20the%20new%20state%20government.%20%26quot%3BAny%20regressive%20policy%20that%20impedes%20the%20growth%20of%20Karnataka%20economically%20and%20is%20going%20to%20take%20the%20state%20backwards%20will%20be%20reviewed%20and%20repealed%20if%20necessary%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20leader%20said%20hinting%20at%20the%20hijab%20ban%20and%20the%20controversial%C2%A0anti-cow%20slaughter%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703260260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-04%2Fdl8l485g_karnataka-hijab-ban_625x300_22_April_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-to-withdraw-hijab-ban-announces-chief-minister-siddaramaiah-4723917%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Karnataka%20government%20on%20Friday%20announced%20it%20will%20soon%20withdraw%20the%20ban%20on%20wearing%20hijab.%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20said%20his%20government%20will%20withdraw%20the%20ban%20soon%2C%20adding%20that%20women%20can%20%26quot%3Bwear%20anything%20they%20want.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-to-withdraw-hijab-ban-announces-chief-minister-siddaramaiah-4723917%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-to-withdraw-hijab-ban-announces-chief-minister-siddaramaiah-4723917%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-to-withdraw-hijab-ban-announces-chief-minister-siddaramaiah-4723917%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Andrew%20Tate%20denied%20request%20to%20visit%20ill%20mother%20in%20UK%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703260129000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F2BB8%2Fproduction%2F_132129111_3f89c252109fafb943fa37ac3927b27ba82e0e75.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67805807%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Andrew%20Tate%20says%20his%20mother%20%26quot%3Bmust%20be%20alone%20at%20Christmas%26quot%3B%20after%20his%20travel%20request%20was%20blocked.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%2