e%20and%20grandfather%20David.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20an%20argument%20with%20my%20mum%20and%20I%20just%20thought%20I'm%20gonna%20leave%20because%20I%20can't%20live%20with%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20reveal%20that%20he%20tried%20persuading%20his%20mother%20to%20move%20to%20a%20rented%20farmhouse%20nearer%20to%20civilisation%20rather%20than%20living%20in%20the%20mountains.%20However%2C%20after%20getting%20tired%20of%20constantly%20moving%20homes%20and%20working%20alongside%20his%20grandfather%20in%20exchange%20for%20food%20and%20rent%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20escape%20his%20mother's%20custody.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2017-year-old%20spoke%20extensively%20about%20his%20escape%20and%20what%20drove%20him%20to%20leave.%20%26quot%3BI%20first%20started%20thinking%20about%20leaving%20when%20I%20was%2014%20or%2015%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20outlet.%20%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20know%20what%20was%20going%20to%20happen%20in%20my%20future%20if%20I%20were%20to%20stay%20with%20my%20mum%2C%20but%20from%20the%20past%20few%20years%20I%20could%20get%20a%20picture%20of%20what%20life%20would%20have%20been%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe's%20a%20great%20person%20and%20I%20love%20her%20but%20she's%20just%20not%20a%20great%20mum%2C%26quot%3B%20Alex%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20teenager%20revealed%20that%20he%20has%20been%20lying%20to%20the%20cops%20to%20protect%20his%20mother%20and%20grandfather.%20%26quot%3BI've%20been%20lying%20to%20try%20and%20protect%20my%20mum%20and%20grandad%20but%20I%20realise%20that%20they're%20probably%20gonna%20get%20caught%20anyway%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Sun%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20get%20lost.%20I%20knew%20exactly%20where%20I%20was%20going%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20describing%20his%20journey%20as%20a%20two-day%20hike%2C%20first%20to%20the%20town%20of%20Quillan%20to%20pretend%20to%20ask%20for%20directions%2C%20then%20on%20towards%20Toulouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fcouple-miraculously-cheats-death-in-separate-plane-crashes-on-the-same-day-4720915%5C%22%3ECouple%20Cheats%20Death%20In%20Separate%20Plane%20Crashes%20On%20The%20Same%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlex%20was%20picked%20up%20by%20a%20delivery%20driver%20who%20spotted%20him%20on%20a%20road%20in%20the%20foothills%20of%20the%20French%20Pyrenees%2C%20near%20Toulouse.%20Fabien%20Accidini%2C%20who%20delivers%20medicines%20to%20pharmacies%20in%20the%20area%2C%20said%20it%20was%20raining%20hard%20when%20he%20picked%20up%20Alex%20Batty%20and%20he%20eventually%20told%20his%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20said%20that%20his%20mother%20had%20kidnapped%20him%20when%20he%20was%20around%2012.%20Since%20then%2C%20he%20has%20lived%20in%20Spain%20in%20a%20luxury%20house%20with%20around%2010%20people.%20He%20would%20have%20arrived%20in%20France%20around%202021.%20He%20had%20lived%20with%20his%20mother%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bspiritual%20community%26quot%3B%20in%20France%20and%20had%20%26quot%3Bno%20animosity%20towards%20her%20but%20wanted%20to%20go%20back%20to%20his%20grandmother%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Accidini%20told%20a%20local%20newspaper.%20He%20also%20helped%20Alex%20contact%20his%20grandmother%20over%20Facebook%20and%20waited%20for%20the%20officers%20to%20arrive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlex%20told%20investigators%20in%20France%20that%20before%20moving%20to%20the%20French%20Pyrenees%2C%20they%20had%20spent%20time%20in%20Morocco.%20The%20report%20added%20that%20for%20the%20past%20six%20years%2C%20Alex%20has%20been%20living%20a%20%26quot%3Bnomadic%26quot%3B%20life%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bspiritual%20community%26quot%3B.%20In%20conversation%20with%20the%20investigators%2C%20the%20teenager%20revealed%20that%20he%20never%20stayed%20in%20the%20same%20place%20for%20more%20than%20several%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20mon