to%20the%20wire%2C%20on%20what%20each%20of%20the%20numbers%20unveiled%20mean.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWho%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EToday%20we%20look%20at%20Lalbegi%20(2%2C720%20people)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20one%20likes%20being%20abused%2C%20but%20the%20Lalbegi%20face%20it%20every%20day.%20T%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eheir%20very%20name%20is%20used%20as%20an%20invective.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20Hindus%2C%20those%20who%20do%20similar%20work%20as%20the%20Lalbegis%20are%20called%20Chuhad.%20At%20some%20places%20they%20are%20also%20called%20Chuhra.%20Derogatorily%20addressing%20them%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echor-chuhad%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20quite%20common%20for%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20people.%20The%20word%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELalbegiya%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20also%20used%20in%20a%20similar%20fashion.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELalbegis%20are%20both%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims.%20It%20is%20possible%20that%20they%20were%20all%20Hindus%20initially%20but%20owing%20to%20caste-based%20discrimination%20and%20antipathy%2C%20they%20converted%20to%20Islam.%20However%2C%20religious%20conversion%20did%20not%20bring%20about%20a%20change%20in%20occupation%20for%20them%20and%20they%20have%2C%20for%20generations%2C%20been%20engaged%20in%20sanitation%20work.%20Even%20today%2C%20people%20belonging%20to%20both%20religions%20are%20sanitation%20workers%20and%20sweepers.%20They%20clean%20roads%20and%20dirty%20drains%2C%20and%20remove%20excreta.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20418px)%2085vw%2C%20418px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22418%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22599%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Hindu%20religion%2C%20they%20are%20addressed%20as%20%E2%80%98Valmiki%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20invoking%20occupation%20they%20are%20also%20called%20%E2%80%98Bhangi%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98Chuhra%E2%80%99.%20Similarly%2C%20upper%20strata%20Muslims%20have%20also%20coined%20a%20new%20term%20and%20address%20them%20as%20%E2%80%98Hasnati%E2%80%99.%20In%20both%20the%20religions%2C%20there%20are%20many%20names%20for%20them%20which%20have%20in%20turn%20become%20various%20castes%20such%20as%20Hela%2C%20Dom%2C%20Halalkhor%2C%20Bhangi%2C%20Chuhra%2C%20Bansphod%2C%20Naamshudra%2C%20Matang%2C%20Mehtar%2C%20Mahar%2C%20Supach%2C%20Beda%2C%20Boya%2C%20Hunter%2C%20Mazhabi%20and%20Koli.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%20sanitation%20work%2C%20they%20also%20make%20various%20bamboo%20items.%20They%20do%20not%20possess%20any%20land%20or%20property.%20There%20might%20be%20a%20few%20people%20in%20the%20community%20who%20own%20property%20or%20capital%20but%20that%20has%20not%20brought%20them%20social%20acceptance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDue%20to%20the%20provision%20of%20reservation%20in%20the%20constitution%2C%20a%20handful%20of%20people%20from%20this%20caste%20group%20have%20managed%20to%20participate%20in%20governance%2C%20but%20there%20has%20been%20no%20change%20in%20their%20social%20status.%20Things%20have%20hardly%20changed%20from%20the%20time%20when%20Dr.%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%2C%20despite%20having%20returned%20after%20studying%20abroad%20and%20accepting%20an%20important%20post%20in%20the%20government%20of%20Baroda%20province%2C%20was%20considered%20a%20Mahar.%20He%20has%20expressed%20his%20painful%20experience%20in%20his%20autobiographical%20account%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWaiting%20for%20a%20Visa%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20one%20might%20ask%20why%20they%20are%20a%20separate%20caste%20group.%20The%20only%20answer%20is%20that%20even%20today%20the%20dominant%20castes%20in%20the%20society%20do%20not%20want%20them%20to%20unite.%20Therefore%2C%20they%20have%20been%20divided%20into%20Lalbegi%20(2%2C720)%2C%20Dom%20(263%2C512)%2C%20Halalkhor%20(7%2C611)%20and%20Bhangi%2FValmiki%20(69%2C914).%20The%20untold%20policy%20is%20to%20keep%20them%20from%20uniting%20and%20becoming%20important%20players%20in%20the%20political%20arena.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%20of%20Lalbegi%2C%20Hela%2C%20Dom%2C%20Halalkhor%2C%20Bhangi%2C%20Chuhra%20or%20Bansphod%2C%20they%20are%20sometimes%20referred%20to%20as%20sanitation%20workers.%20But%20is%20it%20not%20a%20kind%20of%20injustice%20to%20them%3F%20Imagine%20how%20it%20would%20affect%20the%20tender%20minds%20of%20children%20of%20these%20families%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELegends%20about%20their%20origin%20have%20been%20concocted%20by%20both%20Muslims%20and%20Hindus.%20But%20they%20do%20not%20establish%20the%20origin%20of%20Lalbegis.%20The%20religious%20texts%20in%20Islam%20contain%20nothing%20about%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20similar%20things%20have%20been%20said%20in%20Hindu%20religion%20as%20well.%20However%2C%20one%20member%20of%20the%20Chuhra%20caste%2C%20Valmiki%2C%20was%20honoured%20as%20the%20author%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamayana%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20These%20were%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20attempts%20to%20Brahminise%20this%20caste.%20Otherwise%2C%20how%20and%20why%20would%20the%20Brahmins%2C%20who%20could%20not%20think%20of%20a%20decent%20name%20for%20the%20caste%20and%20could%20not%20even%20bear%20to%20step%20into%20the%20shadows%20of%20its%20members%2C%20read%20the%20writings%20of%20Valmiki%3F%20Where%20did%20the%20concept%20of%20untouchability%20go%20then%3F%20Valmiki%20might%20have%20belonged%20to%20some%20other%20caste%20and%20the%20Brahmins%20fabricated%20the%20story%20about%20him%20being%20a%20sweeper%2C%20to%20keep%20the%20caste%20group%20connected%20to%20Hinduism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20efforts%20may%20have%20taken%20place%20after%20the%20arrival%20of%20Muslims%20in%20India%2C%20when%20fed%20up%20with%20the%20oppression%20and%20atrocities%20caused%20due%20to%20discrimination%20in%20Hinduism%2C%20some%20of%20the%20people%20of%20these%20caste%20groups%20must%20have%20converted%20to%20Islam.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20present%20situation%20is%20that%20despite%20being%20categorised%20as%20Scheduled%20Caste%20under%20the%20constitution%2C%20Lalbegi%2C%20Hela%2C%20Dom%2C%20Halalkhor%2C%20Bhangi%2C%20Chuhra%2C%20Bansphod%2C%20Naamshudra%2C%20Matang%2C%20Mehtar%2C%20Mahar%2C%20Supach%2C%20Beda%2C%20Boya%2C%20Hunter%20and%20Koli%2C%20are%20not%20united.%20It%20was%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20dream%20for%20all%20such%20caste%20groups%20to%20unite%20and%20agitate.%20Today%2C%20people%20of%20these%20castes%20worship%20him%2C%20but%20they%20have%20forgotten%20his%20basic%20teaching%2C%20%E2%80%9CBe%20educated%2C%20be%20organised%20and%20struggle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F261402%2Fbihar-caste-survey-lalbegi-caste-society%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20earlier%20parts%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20following%20communities%20by%20clicking%20on%20their%20names%3A%2