20innovation%2Fideas.%20Overall%2C%20it%20may%20be%20true%20that%20the%20US%20has%20dominated%20the%20innovation%20landscape%20for%20much%20of%20the%20past%20half%20a%20century.%20But%20it%20is%20equally%20true%20that%20China%20has%20hugely%20caught%20up%20in%20cutting%20edge%20innovation%20over%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20we%20are%20fundamentally%20opposed%20to%20the%20Chinese%20political%20system%2C%20which%20many%20of%20us%20are%2C%20one%20can%20still%20objectively%20see%20China%E2%80%99s%20big%20strides%20in%20the%20innovation%2Fideas%20space%20which%20has%20led%20to%20it%20closing%20the%20gap%20with%20the%20US%20and%20even%20forge%20ahead%20in%20some%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESometime%20ago%2C%20%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20the%20findings%20of%20an%20independent%20think%20tank%2C%20Australian%20Strategic%20Policy%20Institute%20(ASPI)%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Fchina-leads-us-global-competition-key-emerging-technology-study-says-2023-03-02%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20China%20leads%20the%20world%20in%2037%20out%20of%2044%20critical%20technologies%20in%20the%20field%20of%20defence%2C%20space%2C%20robotics%2C%20energy%2C%20environment%2C%20advanced%20materials%2C%20quantum%20technology%20and%20artificial%20intelligence.%20The%20West%20is%20lagging%20behind%20in%20many%20of%20these%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20Rajan%E2%80%99s%20sweeping%20assertion%20that%20China%20cannot%20be%20a%20leader%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20ideas%20and%20innovation%20is%20not%20borne%20out%20by%20facts%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20such%20massive%20leaps%20of%20progress%20in%20innovation%20is%20happening%20in%20a%20non-democratic%20society%20is%20a%20subject%20for%20a%20separate%20study.%20There%20is%20enough%20academic%20literature%20to%20suggest%20that%20much%20of%20incremental%C2%A0%20growth%20and%20prosperity%20in%20the%2021st%20century%20are%20being%20produced%20by%20societies%20which%20are%20governed%20by%20either%20authoritarian%20or%20partially%20democratic%20regimes.%20These%20regimes%20have%20evolved%20their%20own%20hybrid%20versions%20of%20State-cum-market-led%20capitalism%20models.%20The%20whole%20notion%20of%20the%2021st%20century%20belonging%20to%20Asia%20seems%20to%20be%20based%20on%20such%20a%20hybrid%20framework%20of%20State-cum-market%20model%20of%20capitalism.%20This%20is%20also%20described%20as%20State%20Capitalism%20by%20many%20political%20scientists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20anything%2C%20the%20US%20seems%20to%20be%20aping%20this%20framework%20with%20its%20hugely%20State-led%20model%20of%20a%20new%20industrial%20policy%20to%20counter%20China%20in%20the%20field%20of%20semiconductor%20chips%20and%20green%20energy%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F10%2F17%2Fhow-the-chips-act-is-aiming-to-restore-a-us-lead-in-semiconductors.html%5C%22%3EUS%E2%80%99s%20Chips%20Act%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.energy.gov%2Flpo%2Finflation-reduction-act-2022%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520President%2527s%2520Inflation%2520Reduction%2520Act%2Cenergy%2520manufacturing%252C%2520and%2520putting%2520the%5C%22%3EInflation%20Reduction%20Act%2C%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20together%20aimed%20at%20delivering%20nearly%20%241%20trillion%20of%20subsidies%20for%20semiconductor%20chips%20and%20green%20transition%2C%20are%20a%20tribute%20to%20China%E2%80%99s%20growing%20influence%20in%20these%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20also%20stunned%20the%20world%20recently%20with%20a%20new%2C%20highly%20sophisticated%20semiconductor%20chip%20technology%20for%20electronics%2C%20which%20may%20obviate%20its%20need%20to%20depend%20on%20inputs%20from%20the%20West%20incrementally.%20This%20was%20widely%20reported%20in%20the%20global%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYangtze%20Memory%20Technologies%20Corp%2C%20which%20was%20added%20to%20the%20US%20trade%20blacklist%20last%20December%2C%20made%20a%20%E2%80%9Csurprise%20technology%20leap%E2%80%9D%20through%20a%20solid-state%20drive%20(ZhiTai%20Ti600%201TB)%20launched%20in%20July%20without%20much%20fanfare.%20What%20turns%20that%20from%20surprising%20to%20significant%20is%20the%20fact%20that%203D%20NAND%20memory%20is%20an%20essential%20component%20for%20high-performance%20computing%20(HPC)%2C%20such%20as%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%2C%20%E2%80%9D%20says%20%3Cem%3ETechwire%20Asia%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20tech%20news%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20it%20may%20not%20be%20easy%20to%20write%20off%20China%20as%20merely%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20old%20economy%20and%20a%20laggard%20in%20innovation%20and%20new%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20person%20who%20read%20the%20writing%20on%20the%20wall%20very%20early%20was%20Henry%20Kissinger%2C%20former%20US%20secretary%20of%20State%2C%20who%20passed%20away%20recently.%20In%20one%20of%20his%20visits%20to%20Delhi%2015%20years%20ago%2C%20Kissinger%20told%20a%20group%20of%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20journalists%20in%20an%20off%20the%20record%20chat%20(I%20was%20present)%20that%20China%20was%20forging%20ahead%20of%20the%20US%20in%20many%20critical%20areas%20of%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghuram%20Rajan%20further%20makes%20the%20argument%20that%20the%20US%20keeps%20reinventing%20itself%20via%20innovation%2C%20starting%20from%20the%20Sputnik%20moment%20when%20the%20Soviets%20launched%20the%20first%20artificial%20satellite%2C%20Sputnik%20I.%20The%20successful%20launch%20came%20as%20a%20shock%20to%20the%20US%20as%20it%20had%20hoped%20to%20be%20the%20first%20to%20accomplish%20this%20scientific%20feat.%20However%2C%20the%20US%20came%20from%20behind%20to%20more%20than%20match%20the%20Soviets%20in%20this%20field.%20Later%2C%20in%20the%201980s%20and%201990s%2C%C2%A0%20the%20US%20overcame%20the%20Japanese%20threat%20of%20taking%20leadership%20in%20the%20export%20of%20manufacturing%20sophisticated%20electronics%2C%20automobiles%2C%20etc.%3Cbr%3E%5CnNow%2C%20the%20US%20is%20dealing%20with%20the%20Chinese%20threat%20via%20innovation%20in%20green%20transition%20and%20semiconductor%20chips%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20closer%20scrutiny%20suggests%20that%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20US%20overcame%20these%20threats%20partly%20through%20coercion%20and%20deploying%20its%20geopolitical%20muscle.%20Remember%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.investopedia.com%2Farticles%2Fforex%2F09%2Fplaza-accord.asp%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Plaza%2520Accord%2520was%2520an%2Cthe%2520country%2527s%2520%2522lost%2520decade.%2522%5C%22%3EPlaza%20Accord%20of%201985%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20forced%20Japan%20to%20make%20its%20own%20currency%20more%20expensive%2C%20thereby%20hitting%20Japan%E2%80%99s%20exports%20in%20the%20late%201980s.%20It%20led%20to%20what%20many%20perceived%20as%20Japan%E2%80%99s%20lost%20decade%20in%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20question%20is%20whether%20the%20US%20has%20the%20same%20geo-political%20dominance%20and%20hegemony%20today%20to%20do%20to%20China%20what%20it%20did%20to%20Japan%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20or%20even%20more%20importantly%2C%20what%20it%20did%20to%20the%20Soviets%20in%20the%20second%20half%20of%20the%2020th%20century%3F%20What%20is%20clear%20is%20that%20the%20game%20of%20thrones%20in%20critical%2C%20cutting%20edge%20technologies%20have%20acquired%20totally%20new%20dynamics%20in%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20in%20which%20the%20growing%20middle%20powers%20are%20asserting%20themselves%20like%20never%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20context%2C%20India%20has%20to%20be%20very%20careful%20about%20how%20it%20aligns%20itself%20in%20the%20collaborative%20technology%20framework%C2%A0%20globally.%20It%20may%20be%20a%20mistake%20for%20India%20to%20become%20part%20of%20the%20proposed%20US-India%20critical%20tech%20corridor%20to%20the%20exclusion%20of%20possible%20collaborations%20elsewhere.%20It%20will%20go%20against%20its%20overall%20%E2%80%9Cmulti-alignment%E2%80%9D%20foreign%20policy%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgreenfdc.org%2Fgreen-public-transport-innovation-in-china-an-opportunity-for-bri-countries%2F%5C%22%3Egreen%20transition%20for%20transportation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20China%20is%20way%20ahead%20of%20the%20US%20as%20it%20controls%2080%25%20of%20the%20global%20supply%20chain.%20India%E2%80%99s%20auto%20sector%20which%20has%20developed%20a%20solid%20manufacturing%20supply%20chain%20ecosystem%20over%20the%20last%20three%20decades%20can%20easily%20collaborate%20with%20China%20for%20the%20transformation%20of%20its%20electric%20vehicle%20industry.%20It%20can%20collaborate%20with%20the%20US%20on%20other%20cutting%20edge%20technologies.%20Putting%20all%20eggs%20in%20the%20US%20basket%20may%20not%20be%20wise%20given%20the%20way%20multiple%20technology%20regimes%20are%20shaping%20up%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20century%20may%20not%20produce%20the%20same%20patterns%20as%20the%20previous%20one%20in%20terms%20of%20US%E2%80%99s%20dominance%2C%20whatever%20the%20political%20system%20various%20powers%20are%20operating%20in.%20The%20reality%20is%20critical%20technology%20development%20is%20becoming%20more%20delinked%20from%20the%20nature%20of%20political%20systems%2C%20unlike%20what%20Raghuram%20Rajan%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20that%20matter%20even%20the%20famed%20democratic%20political%20systems%20of%20the%20West%2C%20which%20were%20held%20up%20as%20exemplars%20of%20the%2020th%20century%2C%20seem%20to%20be%20in%20somewhat%20uncharted%20territory%20today%20as%20they%20erode%20pluralist%20ethos%20via%20bottom%20up%20democratic%20processes.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20larger%20battle%20for%20the%20values%20of%20freedom%20and%20openness%20will%20continue%20both%20within%20nations%20and%20transnationally.%20But%20such%20battles%20may%20be%20shaped%20somewhat%20differently%20with%20some%20key%20influences%20deriving%20from%20the%20new%2021st%20century%20alignments%20of%20geopolitics%20and%20geoeconomics.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703246404000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F09085822%2F24939411081_39dd945cb2_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fit-may-be-a-mistake-to-dismiss-china-as-copy-paste%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Must%20wake%20up%20and%20smell%20the%20coffee%20on%20what%20is%20going%20on%20in%20the%20middle%20kingdom%20after%20the%20chip%20war.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fit-may-be-a-mistake-to-dismiss-china-as-copy-paste%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LIVE%3A%20Forex%20reserves%20jump%20by%20%249.11%20bn%20to%20%24615.97%20bn%20for%20week%20ending%20Dec%2015%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703245789000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2018-04%2F15%2Ffull%2F1523813089-1292.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Flatest-news-live-22-december-todays-breaking-news-updates-123122200112_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Catch%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20across%20the%20globe%20here%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Flatest-news-live-22-december-todays-breaking-news-updates-123122200112_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Flatest-news-live-22-december-todays-breaking-news-updates-123122200112_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Flatest-news-live-22-december-todays-breaking-news-updates-123122200112_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Agritec