%20forcibly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20October%207%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Freliefweb.int%2Freport%2Foccupied-palestinian-territory%2Fhostilities-gaza-strip-and-israel-flash-update-73-enarhe%5C%22%3Elarge%20numbers%20of%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Palestinians%3C%2Fspan%3E%20were%20killed%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20settlers%20and%20soldiers%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20many%20of%20them%20were%20civilians.%20One%20of%20them%20is%20the%20Palestinian%20economist%20who%20was%20shot%20in%20his%20forehead%20in%202016%20by%20the%20soldiers%20and%20was%20shot%20to%20death%20by%20settlers%20during%20the%20funeral%20procession%20of%20other%20residents%20from%20his%20village%20who%20were%20killed%20earlier%20%E2%80%93%20also%20by%20settlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhenever%20there%20was%20a%20serious%20incident%20in%20the%20village%2C%20he%20would%20call%20me%20to%20ask%20if%20I%20could%20help%20but%20in%20most%20cases%20I%20was%20not%20able%20to%20do%20anything%20as%20a%20lawyer.%20After%20reports%20began%20to%20be%20published%20on%20social%20media%20that%20some%20Palestinians%20were%20killed%20during%20a%20funeral%20procession%20in%20the%20village%20and%20he%20did%20not%20call%20me%2C%20I%20called%20one%20of%20his%20friends%2C%20another%20Palestinian%20from%20this%20village%20who%20I%20helped%20when%20he%20was%20himself%20shot%20by%20soldiers%20and%20seriously%20injured%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%20Right%20away%2C%20when%20he%20answered%20his%20phone%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20him.%20The%20settlers%20killed%20him%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20story%20is%20not%20unique%2C%20many%20Palestinians%20are%20victims%20of%20multiple%20attacks%20by%20settlers%20and%20soldiers%2C%20and%20there%20is%20often%20an%20overlap%20between%20them.%20If%20the%20soldiers%20are%20not%20settlers%20themselves%2C%20they%20often%20act%20in%20coordination%20and%20under%20the%20instructions%20of%20the%20settlers.%20Even%20if%20a%20Palestinian%20is%20not%20involved%20in%20politics%20or%20one%20of%20the%20armed%20groups%2C%20by%20the%20very%20fact%20of%20being%20a%20Palestinian%20his%20life%20is%20like%20a%20game%20of%C2%A0%20Russian%20Roulette.%20If%20he%20leaves%20his%20house%20to%20work%2C%20to%20the%20field%2C%20to%20study%20or%20to%20visit%20friends%2C%20he%20takes%20a%20gamble%2C%20but%20staying%20locked%20in%20the%20house%20is%20also%20a%20risk%20because%20the%20soldiers%20or%20the%20settlers%20or%20both%20can%20get%20there%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20rise%20in%20violence%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20President%20Biden%20could%20have%20added%20to%20the%20US%20sanctions%20list%20members%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20government%20and%20coalition%20in%20the%20Knesset%20who%20openly%20support%20genocide%2C%20terrorism%20and%20full%20apartheid%2C%20or%20senior%20Israeli%20officials%20who%20approve%20the%20demolition%20of%20Palestinian%20homes%20and%20the%20establishment%20of%20new%20buildings%20in%20the%20settlements%2C%20or%20prevent%20the%20use%20of%20American%20weapons%20by%20specific%20Israeli%20military%20and%20special%20units%20that%20commit%20war%20crimes%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20including%20torture%20and%20extra%20judicial%20killings%2C%20or%20add%20their%20commanders%20to%20the%20sanctions%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kan.org.il%2Fcontent%2Fkan-news%2Fpolitic%2F654899%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edelaying%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20shipment%20of%20more%20than%2027%2C000%20guns%20to%20Israel.%20This%20is%20intended%20for%20the%20police%2C%20which%20is%20under%20the%20full%20control%20of%20the%20far-right%20minister%20Itamar%20Ben%20Gvir.%20This%20is%20because%20of%20the%20fear%20that%20the%20guns%20will%20reach%20violent%20settlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%20is%20expected%20to%20have%20zero%20effect%20on%20Israel.%20Israeli%20companies%20are%20among%20the%20leading%20manufacturers%20of%20rifles%2C%20machine%20guns%20and%20pistols%20in%20the%20world.%20For%20example%2C%20during%20the%20Philippine%20President%20Rodrigo%20Duterte%E2%80%99s%20deadly%20and%20illegal%20%E2%80%9Cwar%20on%20drugs%E2%80%9D%2C%20between%202016%20and%202022%2C%20the%20Israeli%20government%20and%20companies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flobelog.com%2Fisrael-is-trying-to-hide-its-arms-sales-to-dutertes-philippines%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20his%20police%20at%20least%2040%2C000%20rifles%2C%20machine%20guns%20and%20pistols.%20This%20is%20a%20cheap%20military%20equipment%20that%20the%20Israeli%20government%20has%20no%20problem%20purchasing%20from%20local%20Israeli%20companies%2C%20although%20it%20is%20more%20convenient%20for%20Israel%20to%20receive%20it%20freely%20from%20the%20US%20as%20part%20of%20its%20aid%20funds.%20Some%20of%20the%20Israeli%20police%20and%20the%20military%20forces%20already%20use%20Israeli%20manufactured%20rifles%20and%20pistoles.%20If%20necessary%2C%20Israel%20can%20also%20obtain%20the%20Israeli%20guns%20from%20the%20factories%20that%20produce%20them%20abroad%20such%20as%20in%20Vietnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20can%20imagine%20a%20conversation%20between%20President%20Biden%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Netanyahu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%3A%20Bibi%2C%20the%20progressives%20call%20me%20%E2%80%9Cgenocide%20Joe%E2%80%9D%2C%20I%20have%20to%20look%20tough%20with%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%3A%20Don%E2%80%99t%20worry%2C%20cut%20the%20guns%20to%20Ben%20Gvir%20but%20continue%20with%20the%20deliveries%20of%20bombs%20for%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703241025000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F22175839%2FUntitled-design-9.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbiden-guns-shipment-delay-israel%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20decision%20is%20expected%20to%20have%20zero%20effect%20on%20Israel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%