%2C%20or%20prevent%20the%20use%20of%20American%20weapons%20by%20specific%20Israeli%20military%20and%20special%20units%20that%20commit%20war%20crimes%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20including%20torture%20and%20extra%20judicial%20killings%2C%20or%20add%20their%20commanders%20to%20the%20sanctions%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kan.org.il%2Fcontent%2Fkan-news%2Fpolitic%2F654899%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edelaying%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20shipment%20of%20more%20than%2027%2C000%20guns%20to%20Israel.%20This%20is%20intended%20for%20the%20police%2C%20which%20is%20under%20the%20full%20control%20of%20the%20far-right%20minister%20Itamar%20Ben%20Gvir.%20This%20is%20because%20of%20the%20fear%20that%20the%20guns%20will%20reach%20violent%20settlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%20is%20expected%20to%20have%20zero%20effect%20on%20Israel.%20Israeli%20companies%20are%20among%20the%20leading%20manufacturers%20of%20rifles%2C%20machine%20guns%20and%20pistols%20in%20the%20world.%20For%20example%2C%20during%20the%20Philippine%20President%20Rodrigo%20Duterte%E2%80%99s%20deadly%20and%20illegal%20%E2%80%9Cwar%20on%20drugs%E2%80%9D%2C%20between%202016%20and%202022%2C%20the%20Israeli%20government%20and%20companies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flobelog.com%2Fisrael-is-trying-to-hide-its-arms-sales-to-dutertes-philippines%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20his%20police%20at%20least%2040%2C000%20rifles%2C%20machine%20guns%20and%20pistols.%20This%20is%20a%20cheap%20military%20equipment%20that%20the%20Israeli%20government%20has%20no%20problem%20purchasing%20from%20local%20Israeli%20companies%2C%20although%20it%20is%20more%20convenient%20for%20Israel%20to%20receive%20it%20freely%20from%20the%20US%20as%20part%20of%20its%20aid%20funds.%20Some%20of%20the%20Israeli%20police%20and%20the%20military%20forces%20already%20use%20Israeli%20manufactured%20rifles%20and%20pistoles.%20If%20necessary%2C%20Israel%20can%20also%20obtain%20the%20Israeli%20guns%20from%20the%20factories%20that%20produce%20them%20abroad%20such%20as%20in%20Vietnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20can%20imagine%20a%20conversation%20between%20President%20Biden%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Netanyahu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%3A%20%E2%80%9CBibi%2C%20the%20progressives%20call%20me%20%E2%80%9Cgenocide%20Joe%E2%80%9D%2C%20I%20have%20to%20look%20tough%20with%20you%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%3A%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20worry%2C%20cut%20the%20guns%20to%20Ben%20Gvir%20but%20continue%20with%20the%20deliveries%20of%20bombs%20for%20Gaza%E2%80%9D.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703241025000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11160252%2FGA6xi9-WoAEKSsS.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbetter-late-than-never-global-powers-must-force-israel-to-pursue-diplomatic-means-to-fight-hamas%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20decision%20is%20expected%20to%20have%20zero%20effect%20on%20Israel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbetter-late-than-never-global-powers-must-force-israel-to-pursue-diplomatic-means-to-fight-hamas%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20and%20Nicaragua%20sign%20loan%20for%20international%20airport%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703240944000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106211545%2Cimgsize-1112533.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-and-nicaragua-sign-loan-for-international-airport%2Farticleshow%2F106211391.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106211391.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ENicaragua%20signs%20%24430%