arate%20bedrooms%20-%20or%20even%20different%20houses%20-%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Bnormalised%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A247%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fcameron-diaz-says-long-term-couples-sleeping-in-separate-bedrooms-should-be-normalised-13036194%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fcameron-diaz-says-long-term-couples-sleeping-in-separate-bedrooms-should-be-normalised-13036194%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fcameron-diaz-says-long-term-couples-sleeping-in-separate-bedrooms-should-be-normalised-13036194%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Protest%20at%20the%20Parliament%20Should%20Be%20Seen%20as%20Fearlessness%2C%20Not%20Terror%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20never%20fails%20to%20amuse%20me%20is%20the%20unbearable%20pomposity%2C%20the%20self-absorption%2C%20and%20the%20conceit%20of%20our%20representatives%20in%20the%20parliament.%20Two%20young%20people%20protested%2C%20in%20an%20admittedly%20unusual%20manner%2C%20by%20releasing%20plumes%20of%20yellow%20smoke%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Two%20more%20were%20part%20of%20this%20audacious%20plan.%20They%20believe%20that%20politics%20is%20the%20art%20of%20the%20impossible.%20And%20they%20showed%20us%20how.%20But%20%E2%80%98august%E2%80%99%20members%20of%20the%20parliament%2C%20scuttling%20here%20and%20there%20to%20escape%20%E2%80%98poisonous%20gas%E2%80%99%2C%20have%20typed%20the%20intrusion%20as%20nothing%20less%20than%20an%20attack%20on%20national%20security.%20Seriously%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20that%20four%20young%20people%20were%20trying%20to%20do%20is%20to%20make%20us%20hear%2C%20in%20a%20rather%20dramatic%20fashion%20%3Cem%3Ea%20la%3C%2Fem%3E%20Bhagat%20Singh%2C%20was%20their%20voice%20of%20pain%2C%20despair%2C%20and%20frustration.%20They%20made%20an%20unexpected%20entry%20into%20the%20House%2C%20simply%20because%20they%20wanted%20their%20representatives%20and%20their%20country%20to%20heed%20their%20justifiable%20protest%20at%20unemployment%2C%20deprivation%2C%20and%20despondency.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20else%20could%20they%20have%20done%3F%20Their%20voices%20are%20just%20not%20heard%20by%20those%20who%20strut%20the%20corridors%20of%20power.%20Demonstrations%20are%20frowned%20upon%2C%20dissent%20suppressed%2C%20and%20alternative%20visions%20of%20politics%20dismissed%20as%20the%20work%20of%20anti-nationals.%20When%20people%20do%20not%20have%20access%20to%20any%20channel%20to%20express%20grievances%2C%20politics%20takes%20to%20the%20streets%2C%20or%20in%20this%20case%2C%20right%20into%20parliament.%20This%20is%20the%20lesson%20of%20politics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpangs-of-unemployment-why-indias-youth-is-turning-to-bhagat-singh%5C%22%3EPangs%20of%20Unemployment%3A%20Why%20India%E2%80%99s%20Youth%20is%20Turning%20to%20Bhagat%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConsider%20the%20background%3B%20abject%20poverty.%20The%20prime%20minister%20has%20announced%20the%20extension%20of%20free%20rations%20to%2081%20crore%20Indians.%20The%20implication%20is%20that%20millions%20of%20our%20fellow%20citizen%20go%20to%20bed%20hungry.%20Not%20a%20pretty%20picture%20for%20a%20country%20that%20is%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%98atma%20nirbhar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(self%20sufficient)%2C%20least%20of%20all%20one%20that%20is%20located%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98amrit%20kaal%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20government%20is%20not%20statistic%20friendly.%20So%20we%20do%20not%20know%20how%20many%20people%20fall%20below%20the%20poverty%20line%2C%20or%20even%20what%20the%20poverty%20line%20is.%20But%20if%2081%20crore%20people%20cannot%20buy%20food%20for%20themselves%2C%20the%20deprivation%20they%20are%20mired%20in%20defies%20imagination.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20this%20tragic%20fact%20of%20our%20national%20life%20that%20has%20been%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20policy%20makers%20by%20our%20young%20intruders.%20The%20response%20was%20to%20slap%20the%20UAPA%20upon%20them.%20Consider%20the%20irony.%20The%20majesty%20of%20the%20house%20was%20not%20harmed%20when%20one%20MP%20heaped%20communal%20slurs%20upon%20a%20fellow%20parliamentarian.%20Basic%20notions%20of%20justice%2C%20civility%2C%20and%20gender%20sensitivity%20were%20grossly%20violated%20when%20a%20woman%20MP%20raised%20questions%20related%20to%20national%20wellbeing%20and%20the%20handing%20over%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20resources%20to%20one%20capitalist.%20She%20was%20expelled%20from%20the%20House.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20when%20two%20young%20people%20reenacting%20the%20actions%20of%20their%20hero%20Bhagat%20Singh%20descend%20into%20the%20House%20and%20raise%20uncomfortable%20questions%2C%20the%20majesty%20of%20the%20house%20is%20dented.%20Perhaps%20they%20were%20reclaiming%20%E2%80%98the%20people%E2%80%99%20in%20a%20House%20that%20has%20been%20taken%20over%20by%20the%20ruling%20party%20with%20deleterious%20consequences.%20The%20phrase%20%E2%80%98We%20the%20People%E2%80%99%20is%20empty%20until%20and%20unless%20the%20people%20bring%20the%20malaise%20of%20the%20country%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20ruling%20authorities%20through%20unusual%20actions.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20did%20so%20by%20picking%20up%20a%20handful%20of%20salt%20and%20breaking%20the%20law.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20notion%20of%20the%20people%20presents%20itself%20to%20us%20in%20tangible%20forms%20through%20such%20actions%20performed%20with%20a%20degree%20of%20unmatched%20fearlessness.%20We%20would%20do%20well%20to%20recollect%20that%20Gandhi%20had%20written%20that%20%E2%80%9CI%20hope%20also%20to%20achieve%20the%20end%20by%20demonstrating%20that%20real%20%3Cem%3Eswaraj%3C%2Fem%3E%20will%20come%20not%20by%20the%20acquisition%20of%20authority%20by%20a%20few%20but%20by%20the%20acquisition%20of%20the%20capacity%20by%20all%20to%20resist%20authority%20when%20it%20is%20abused.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20swaraj%20is%20to%20be%20attained%20by%20educating%20the%20masses%20to%20a%20sense%20of%20their%20capacity%20to%20regulate%20and%20control%20authority%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30082243%2FIMG_1748.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30082243%2FIMG_1748.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30082243%2FIMG_1748-300x210.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30082243%2FIMG_1748-1024x715.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-638156%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22838%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20precisely%20this%20aspect%20of%20politics%2C%20of%20educating%20the%20people%20into%20a%20sense%20of%20their%20own%20capacity%20to%20regulate%20and%20control%20authority%2C%20that%20is%20repressed%20by%20authoritarian%20governments.%20They%20dream%20of%20a%20society%20where%20no%20one%20dare%20speak%20or%20act%20against%20the%20supreme%20leader%2C%20only%20acclaim%20him.%20Hannah%20Arendt%20in%20her%20famous%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Human%20Condition%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20(1958)%2C%C2%A0%20had%20written%20that%20exasperation%20with%20the%20three%20fold%20frustration%20of%20action%3A%20the%20unpredictability%20of%20its%20outcome%2C%20the%20irreversibility%20of%20the%20process%2C%20and%20the%20anonymity%20of%20its%20authors%2C%20leads%20to%20the%20denouncement%20of%20action%20and%20speech%20in%20particular%2C%20and%20politics%20in%20action.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20always%20been%20a%20great%20temptation%2C%20for%20men%20of%20action%20no%20less%20than%20for%20men%20of%20thought%2C%20to%20find%20a%20substitute%20for%20action%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20the%20realm%20of%20human%20affairs%20may%20escape%20the%20haphazardness%20and%20moral%20irresponsibility%20inherent%20in%20a%20plurality%20of%20agents.%E2%80%9D%20This%20is%20as%20old%20as%20recorded%20history.%20Generally%20speaking%2C%20such%20men%20seek%20shelter%20from%20popular%20politics%2C%20that%20can%20go%20this%20way%20or%20that%2C%20by%20dreaming%20of%20a%20society%20where%20one%20man%2C%20isolated%20from%20all%20others%2C%20remains%20master%20of%20his%20doings%20from%20beginning%20to%20end.%20This%20attempt%20to%20replace%20acting%20with%20making%20is%20manifest%20in%20the%20whole%20body%20of%20argument%20against%20%E2%80%98democracy%E2%80%99%2C%20which%2C%20the%20more%20consistently%20and%20better%20reasoned%20it%20is%2C%20will%20turn%20into%20an%20argument%20against%20the%20essentials%20of%20politics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArendt%20was%20prescient%2C%20and%20this%20is%20an%20understatement.%20The%20politics%20of%20impossibility%20represented%20as%20thought%20and%20action%20in%20the%20public%20realm%20is%20plural%20and%20contested.%20What%20is%20not%20contested%2C%20is%20not%20politics.%20But%20this%20is%20not%20acceptable%20to%20our%20rulers.%20They%20attempt%20to%20do%20away%20with%20politics%20by%20doing%20away%20with%20the%20public%20sphere.%20And%20%E2%80%98we%20the%20people%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20have%20sadly%20helped%20them%20by%20constituting%20ourselves%20as%20subjects%20of%20a%20ruler%2C%20not%20as%20citizens%20of%20a%20democracy%20that%20have%20the%20right%20to%20call%20the%20government%20to%20account.%20We%20are%20told%20to%20attend%20to%20our%20personal%20affairs%20and%20perform%20duties.%20The%20business%20of%20politics%20is%20best%20left%20to%20power.%20And%20we%20do%20so.%20I%20am%20afraid%20that%20we%20as%20the%20people%20have%20played%20the%20game%20of%20the%20holders%20of%20power.%20We%20have%20retreated%20from%20the%20public%20sphere%20into%20the%20private%2C%20armed%20with%20the%20blissful%20conviction%20that%20a%20group%20of%20men%20can%20take%20care%20of%20us%2C%20and%20of%20politics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20have%20lost%20our%20memory%20of%20resistance%20and%20struggle.%20The%20reduction%20of%20Gandhi%20to%20a%20pair%20of%20spectacles%20has%20proved%20disastrous.%20His%20politics%20has%20been%20reduced%20from%20the%20subversive%20to%20the%20routine%3B%20picking%20up%20the%20broom%20and%20cleaning%20the%20streets.%20Gandhi%2C%20it%20is%20true%2C%20cleaned%20toilets%20at%20the%20meetings%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress.%20But%20he%20did%20much%20more.%20As%20a%20man%20of%20the%20moment%2C%20he%20was%20skilled%20in%20the%20art%20of%20crafting%20political%20strategy.%20He%20showed%20us%20how%20to%20be%20courageous%20and%20fearless.%20%E2%80%98I%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9Chave%20been%20collecting%20descriptions%20of%20s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewaraj%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20One%20of%20these%20is%20the%20abandonment%20of%20the%20fear%20of%20death.%20%E2%80%9CA%20nation%20which%20allows%20itself%20to%20be%20influenced%20by%20the%20fear%20of%20death%20cannot%20attain%20swaraj%2C%20and%20cannot%20retain%20it%20if%20somehow%20obtained.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%20do%20we%20not%20see%20these%20young%20intruders%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20as%20fearless%3F%20They%20knew%20the%20consequences%20of%20their%20action.%20Think%20of%20their%20profound%20disappointment%20when%20they%20realised%20that%20the%20people%20they%20had%20elected%20to%20parliament%2C%20who%20luxuriate%20in%20the%20power%20that%20the%20status%20bestows%20upon%20them%2C%20were%20supremely%20indifferent%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20their%20own%20people.%20They%20might%20well%20have%20said-we%20asked%20for%20jobs%2C%20we%20got%20temples%20instead.%20They%20reacted%20in%20the%20only%20way%20they%20could%20%E2%80%93%20with%20courage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fneera-chandhoke%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ENeera%20Chandhoke%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%20was%20a%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20at%20Delhi%20University.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703239501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fprotest-at-the-parliament-should-be-seen-as-fearlessness-not-terror%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Think%20of%20the%20youth's%20profound%20disappointment%20when%20they%20realised%20that%20the%20people%20they%20had%20elected%20to%20parliament%20were%20supremely%20indifferent%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20their%20own%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fprotest-at-the-parliament-should-be-seen-as-fearlessness-not-terror%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CISF%20Asked%20to%20Take%20Over%20Parliament%20Security%20After%20Breach%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26191526%2F1280px-View_of_Lok_Sabha_chamber_in_the_New_Parliament_building_New_Delhi.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20home%20ministry%20has%20asked%20the%20Central%20Industrial%20Security%20Force%20(CISF)%20to%20conduct%20a%20survey%20of%20the%20parliament%20to%20establish%20%E2%80%9Cregular%20deployment%20on%20a%20comprehensive%20pattern%E2%80%9D%2C%20days%20after%20a%20security%20breach%20occurred%20on%20the%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmha-parliament-cisf-security-breach-9077141%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20CISF%20will%20collaborate%20with%20Parliament%20Security%20Services%20to%20regulate%20access%20to%20both%20the%20old%20and%20new%20parliament%20complex.%20Currently%2C%20visitor%20frisking%20is%20managed%20by%20Delhi%20Police%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2013%2C%20two%20individuals%20with%20smoke%20cans%20jumped%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20chamber%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpangs-of-unemployment-why-indias-youth-is-turning-to-bhagat-singh%5C%22%3Estage%20a%20protest%20against%20rising%20unemployment%2C%20inflation%20and%20poverty%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20were%20accompanied%20by%20two%20others%20who%20remained%20outside%20and%20yelled%20slogans%20like%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9Ctanshahi%20nahi%20chalegi%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eand%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9Cbharat%20mata%20ki%20jai%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20breach%20prompted%20a%20preliminary%20probe%20by%20a%20committee%2C%20headed%20by%20CRPF%20Director%20General%20Anish%20Dayal%20Singh%2C%20which%20identified%20security%20lapses%20during%20visitor%20frisking.%20Subsequently%2C%20eight%20security%20personnel%20were%20suspended%2C%20the%3Cem%3E%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmha-parliament-cisf-security-breach-9077141%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20internal%20communication%2C%20MHA%20Under%20Secretary%20Ashutosh%20Kumar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmha-parliament-cisf-security-breach-9077141%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn-principle%20approval%20of%20the%20competent%20authority%20is%20conveyed%20for%20carrying%20out%20the%20survey%20of%20the%20Parliament%20premises%20and%20its%20building%20for%20regular%20deployment%20of%20CISF%20%E2%80%93%20both%20security%20wing%20and%20fire%20wing%20%E2%80%93%20on%20comprehensive%20pattern%20under%20Government%20Building%20Security%20(GBS).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CISF%20has%20initiated%20a%20joint%20survey%20by%20its%20Government%20Building%20Security%20unit%20and%20fire%20wing%20to%20ascertain%20the%20exact%20number%20of%20personnel%20needed%20and%20define%20the%20role%20of%20each%20security%20agency%20involved%20in%20Parliament%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20letter%20from%20a%20DIG-rank%20officer%20outlined%20the%20constitution%20of%20a%20joint%20survey%20board%2C%20with%20Ajay%20Kumar%2C%20DIG%2C%20CISF%20Unit%20CGBS%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20as%20the%20presiding%20officer.%20The%20board%20is%20tasked%20with%20conducting%20the%20survey%20in%20association%20with%20representatives%20of%20the%20parliament%20secretariat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpangs-of-unemployment-why-indias-youth-is-turning-to-bhagat-singh%5C%22%3EPangs%20Of%20Unemployment%3A%20Why%20India%E2%80%99s%20Youth%20Is%20Turning%20To%20Bhagat%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20board%20is%20directed%20to%20submit%20completed%20reports%20for%20Security%20and%20Fire%20Wing%2C%20including%20information%20proforma%20and%20IFD%20chart%20with%20specific%20justifications%20for%20each%20duty%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20pursuance%20of%20MHA%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98in-principle%E2%80%99%20approval%2C%20board%20for%20conducting%20joint%20survey%20of%20Parliament%20premises%20and%20its%20buildings%20for%20regular%20deployment%20of%20CISF%20Security%20and%20Fire%20Wing%20on%20comprehensive%20pattern%2C%20as%20per%20PSU%20and%20fire%20norms%2C%20is%20hereby%20constituted%20with%20Ajay%20Kumar%2C%20DIG%2C%20CISF%20Unit%20CGBS%2C%20New%20Delhi%20as%20presiding%20officer.%20It%20is%20requested%20to%20detail%20other%20members%20of%20the%20joint%20survey%20board%20including%20an%20officer%20with%20technical%20expertise.%20An%20officer%20of%20CISF%20Fire%20Wing%20may%20also%20be%20detailed%20in%20consultation%20with%20the%20Fire%20Directorate.%20The%20survey%20board%20may%20be%20directed%20to%20conduct%20the%20survey%20(as%20per)%20instructions%2F%20guidelines%20issued%20from%20time%20to%20time%20on%20conducting%20surveys%20in%20association%20with%20representative(s)%20of%20the%20Parliament%20Secretariat%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmha-parliament-cisf-security-breach-9077141%2F%5C%22%3Eletter%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuly%20completed%20survey%20reports%20for%20Security%20and%20Fire%20Wing%20with%20these%20documents%20may%20kindly%20be%20submitted%20to%20this%20Directorate%20at%20the%20earliest%20for%20further%20process%20please%3B%20information%20proforma%2C%20and%20IFD%20chart%20with%20specific%20justification%20for%20each%20duty%20post%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703239236000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26191526%2F1280px-View_of_Lok_Sabha_chamber_in_the_New_Parliament_building_New_Delhi.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcisf-asked-to-take-over-parliament-security-after-breach%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CISF%20will%20collaborate%20with%20Parliament%20Security%20Services%20to%20regulate%20access%20to%20both%20the%20old%20and%20new%20parliament%20complex.%20Currently%2C%20visitor%20frisking%20is%20managed%20by%20Delhi%20Police%20personnel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcisf-asked-to-take-over-parliament-security-after-breach%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22History%20Repeats%2C%20Twists%20and%20Turns%3A%20Democracy%20Is%20Again%20in%20the%20Doghouse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FCharlie.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EHistory%2C%20we%20have%20been%20instructed%2C%20is%20now%20the%20story%20of%20warfare%2C%20now%20of%20the%20struggle%20for%20existence%2C%20now%20of%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20species%2C%20now%20the%20unfolding%20of%20a%20divine%20idea%2C%20of%20the%20effulgence%20of%20religions%2C%20of%20patriarchy%2C%20of%20class%20struggle%20destined%20through%20the%20unity%20of%20evolving%20contradictions%20to%20reach%20the%20fullness%20of%20justice%20for%20humankind%2C%20the%20progression%20of%20inventions%20and%20technologies%20unleashing%20modernity%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost%20the%20idea%20of%20modernity%2C%20it%20has%20come%20to%20be%20seen%20by%20some%20others%20as%20merely%20an%20ephemeral%20play%20of%20language%20%E2%80%93%20forever%20open-ended%2C%20never%20reaching%20any%20final%20resolution%20or%20meaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ideologue%2C%20Spengler%2C%20proffered%20the%20metaphor%20of%20a%20cartwheel%20for%20history%2C%20holding%20that%20just%20as%20there%20have%20been%20climatic%20earth%20cycles%2C%20there%20are%20also%20political%20cycles%20in%20human%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20just%20as%20in%20the%20rotation%20of%20a%20cartwheel%2C%20the%20point%20that%20touches%20the%20ground%20and%20then%20progresses%20upward%20inevitably%20returns%20to%20touch%20the%20ground%20again%2C%20so%20also%2C%20different%20systemic%20arrangements%20of%20history%20have%20a%20life%2C%20move%20on%2C%20and%20return%20when%20we%20think%20what%20is%20gone%20never%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20consider%20this%3A%20the%20advent%20of%20inductive%20science%20brought%20with%20it%20a%20flush%20of%20enquiry%20and%20possibility%20in%20a%20slew%20of%20human%20thought%20and%20material%20endeavour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20wake%2C%20science%20opened%20up%20a%20market%20of%20both%20ideas%20and%20goods%20and%20services%20for%20capital%20to%20operate%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECapitalism%20in%20its%20burgeoning%20required%20the%20destruction%20of%20old%20feudal%20constraints%20across%20the%20board%2C%20and%20so%20spawned%20the%20idea%20of%20democracy%20as%20an%20idea%2C%20rooted%20in%20the%20productive%20potential%20and%20dignity%20of%20the%20human%20individual.%20But%20when%20it%20came%20into%20full%20ascendance%2C%20Capital%20saw%20that%20science%2C%20which%20had%20brought%20it%20into%20being%20was%20now%20its%20enemy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20it%20required%20was%20technology%2C%20not%20science%2C%20or%20if%20you%20like%2C%20a%20science%20that%20was%20now%20directing%20all%20its%20ingenuity%20not%20to%20explore%20further%20truths%2C%20or%20question%20Capitalism%20and%20the%20social%20order%20it%20came%20to%20spawn%2C%20but%20to%20devise%20newer%20instruments%20for%20generating%20and%20accumulating%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20this%20endeavour%20began%20to%20see%20that%20along%20with%20science%2C%20democracy%20too%20was%20a%20potential%20antagonist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20wealth%20came%20to%20be%20monopolised%2C%20ideas%20of%20social%2C%20economic%20and%20political%20equity%20spelt%20danger%20to%20the%20now%20entrenched%20power%20of%20Capital%20across%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClever%20protagonists%20soon%20saw%20that%20the%20protection%20and%20furtherance%20of%20what%20they%20had%20achieved%20would%20now%20require%20strategies%20for%20quelling%20the%20free%20mental%20agency%20of%20people%20at%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENothing%20could%20achieve%20this%20project%20of%20silencing%20better%20than%20the%20deployment%20of%20race%2C%20religion%20and%20nationalism%2C%20ruthlessly%20propagated%20among%20the%20mass%20of%20people%20through%20facilitations%20made%20available%20by%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitler%20used%20the%20radio%20to%20great%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20the%20relentless%20use%20of%20electronic%20media%2C%20and%20now%20what%20is%20called%20rather%20outlandishly%20the%20%E2%80%98social%20media%E2%80%99%20to%20condition%20the%20%E2%80%98popular%20mind%E2%80%99%20to%20unquestioningly%20receive%20whatever%20the%20posers-that-be%20dish%20out%20in%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20interest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cartwheel%2C%20however%2C%20turned%20after%20the%20defeat%20of%20Fascism%20in%20Europe%2C%20and%20a%20renewed%20liberalism%20seemed%20to%20once%20again%20suffuse%20the%20political%20climate%20of%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20destruction%20wrought%20by%20war%20facilitated%20the%20ingress%20of%20the%20benevolent%20Marshall%20plan%20to%20rebuild%20Europe%20as%20a%20democratic%20enclave%20and%2C%20more%20to%20the%20point%2C%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20market%E2%80%9D%20ready%20to%20receive%20the%20munificence%20of%20American%20productive%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDecolonisation%20across%20continents%20released%20a%20flush%20of%20human%20freedom%20and%20new%20dreams%20among%20the%20oppressed%20peoples%20of%20erstwhile%20slave%20states%2C%20as%20it%20were%2C%20to%20make%20their%20own%20new%20future%20along%20the%20best%20principles%20of%20political%20and%20economic%20liberalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocracy%20once%20again%20became%20a%20desired%20handmaiden%2C%20and%20new%2C%20emancipatory%20constitutions%20came%20to%20be%20fashioned%20in%20so%20many%20decolonised%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20canny%20indigenous%20colonisers%20were%20waiting%20in%20the%20wings%20to%20replicate%20many%20of%20the%20social%2C%20cultural%2C%20and%20political%20strategies%20of%20foreigners%20who%20had%20kept%20these%20realms%20in%20thrall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20now%20look%20around%20you.%20Democracy%20in%20a%20plethora%20of%20countries%20is%20once%20again%20moving%20on%20and%20bringing%20the%20cartwheel%20back%20to%20touch%20the%20ground%20which%20it%20had%20left%20behind%20in%20the%20decades%20of%20the%20thirties%20and%20the%20forties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWherever%20democracy%20is%20retained%20formally%20still%2C%20this%20is%2C%20as%20the%20barber%20double%20of%20Hitler%20in%20Charlie%20Chaplin%E2%80%99s%20masterpiece%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Great%20Dictator%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20perorates%20in%20that%20immortal%20speech%20he%20makes%20to%20the%20masses%2C%20it%20is%20done%20to%20squeamishly%20deflect%20popular%20shame%2C%20as%20did%20the%20fig%20leaf%2C%20while%20intending%20to%20destroy%20it%20soon%20as%20political%20power%20is%20achieved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FJ7GY1Xg6X20%3Fsi%3D1xoFyQ4qzbHtskNA%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20in%20our%20day%2C%20there%20are%20two%20kinds%20of%20democrats%E2%80%94those%20to%20whom%20the%20idea%20of%20democracy%20is%20a%20non-negotiable%20principle%20that%20encapsulates%20the%20march%20through%20historical%20time%20of%20humankind%E2%80%99s%20most%20just%20and%20ethical%20strivings%2C%20and%20those%20to%20whom%20it%20is%20a%20mask%20to%20be%20discarded%20as%20soon%20as%20it%20has%20served%20its%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20wit%2C%20there%20are%20those%20of%20us%20who%20think%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcost-of-suspending-members-of-parliament%5C%22%3E15%20crore%20electors%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20(and%20more%2C%2018%20crore%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha)%20whom%20the%20suspended%20146%20members%20of%20the%20Indian%20parliament%20represent%2C%20are%20equal%20citizens%20of%20the%20republic%20who%20have%20charged%20thei